### [Leviticus Chapter 5](../../../bib/kjv/lev005.htm#001.md)

[Leviticus 5:6](../../../bib/kjv/lev005.htm#006.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_006">lev 5:6</span></span>

trespass offering

The trespass-offerings have in view rather the injury which sin does
than its guilt - which is the sin-offering aspect. What is due to God's
rights in every human being is here meant. ([Psa
51:4](../../../bib/kjv/psa051.htm#004).md); is a perfect expression of
this.

